creator: Marshmallo Dating: Match, Chat, Meet & Date Safely
descriptionHtml:
DON'T GET BURNED. INTUITION IS GOOD. VERIFICATION IS BETTER
Marshmallo verifies every member’s selfie, photo ID and profile pictures, and we exclude over 700,000 registered offenders. Chat with real people and make real relationships. Say good-bye catfish and hello real matches.

WHY SHARE YOUR ID WITH A DATING APP
You share your driver's license to rent a car or apartment, check into a hotel, fly on a plane, see a doctor or open a bank account. Your dating life is just as important. We do not store sensitive data like your driver’s license number or physical address.

SAFETY FEATURES
Registered offender check
ID verification
Selfie verification
Profile photo verification
Harassment protection
Enhanced privacy options

ID VERIFICATION
We verify every member’s photo ID with the same technology that is used by major banks. Everybody you message is a real person with their real name and age. We are the first free dating app to verify the photo ID of every member and check registered offender databases, and we are a proud pioneer in online dating safety.

SELFIE VERIFICATION
Worried about catfishing?
All members take a selfie that we verify against their photo ID and other profile pictures. Worry less about catfishing and enjoy s’more when you use Marshmallo.

PROFILE VERIFICATION
We use artificial intelligence to make sure people’s profile pictures match their selfie and photo portion of their government-issued photo ID. We really don’t like catfishers!

REGISTERED OFFENDER CHECK
According to the FBI, over 1 in 10 registered offenders has an online dating profile. Background checks can be costly, so we check over 700,000 names in over 300 registered offender databases on your behalf. You can be sure that there are no publicly registered offenders on Marshmallo without needing to do a background check.

HARASSMENT PROTECTION
Tired of being harassed?
We stop repeated unwanted messaging before it happens. You can only receive one message from people unless you respond. Make new friends without worrying about people you don’t want to talk to harassing you.

PRIVACY
You have the option to make your religion, political preferences and other information visible only to people with the same answers. Selectively share information so you can get better matches without telling everybody everything about yourself.

FIRST INITIAL
We only share your first initial. Keep your identity to yourself until you feel comfortable sharing it.

FREE TO USE
Marshmallo is free to use. We make money through members who optionally pay for premium features.

HAVE FUN
Safely chat with new friends, meet new people and make new relationships. Marshmallo makes online dating a safer and more fun experience for everyone.

Photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

descriptionHtml:
DON'T GET BURNED. INTUITION IS GOOD. VERIFICATION IS BETTER
Marshmallo verifies every member’s selfie, photo ID and profile pictures, and we exclude over 700,000 registered offenders. Chat with real people and make real relationships. Say good-bye catfish and hello real matches.

WHY SHARE YOUR ID WITH A DATING APP
You share your driver's license to rent a car or apartment, check into a hotel, fly on a plane, see a doctor or open a bank account. Your dating life is just as important. We do not store sensitive data like your driver’s license number or physical address.

SAFETY FEATURES
Registered offender check
ID verification
Selfie verification
Profile photo verification
Harassment protection
Enhanced privacy options

ID VERIFICATION
We verify every member’s photo ID with the same technology that is used by major banks. Everybody you message is a real person with their real name and age. We are the first free dating app to verify the photo ID of every member and check registered offender databases, and we are a proud pioneer in online dating safety.

SELFIE VERIFICATION
Worried about catfishing?
All members take a selfie that we verify against their photo ID and other profile pictures. Worry less about catfishing and enjoy s’more when you use Marshmallo.

PROFILE VERIFICATION
We use artificial intelligence to make sure people’s profile pictures match their selfie and photo portion of their government-issued photo ID. We really don’t like catfishers!

REGISTERED OFFENDER CHECK
According to the FBI, over 1 in 10 registered offenders has an online dating profile. Background checks can be costly, so we check over 700,000 names in over 300 registered offender databases on your behalf. You can be sure that there are no publicly registered offenders on Marshmallo without needing to do a background check.

HARASSMENT PROTECTION
Tired of being harassed?
We stop repeated unwanted messaging before it happens. You can only receive one message from people unless you respond. Make new friends without worrying about people you don’t want to talk to harassing you.

PRIVACY
You have the option to make your religion, political preferences and other information visible only to people with the same answers. Selectively share information so you can get better matches without telling everybody everything about yourself.

FIRST INITIAL
We only share your first initial. Keep your identity to yourself until you feel comfortable sharing it.

FREE TO USE
Marshmallo is free to use. We make money through members who optionally pay for premium features.

HAVE FUN
Safely chat with new friends, meet new people and make new relationships. Marshmallo makes online dating a safer and more fun experience for everyone.

Photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.
